languages.text: "В этом вопросе — рискну. При плохом исходе вы погубите Футфол — ну и к чему мне в этом случае будет ваше доброе расположение?"
"In this matter, I would. If this visit of yours goes awry, it will destroy Footfall — what good will your favour do me then?"
languages.original_text: "В этом вопросе — рискну. При плохом исходе вы погубите Футфол — ну и к чему мне в этом случае будет ваше доброе расположение?"

traits.locale_text: "In this matter — I would. If this visit of yours goes awry, you will devastate Footfall — and what good will your favour do me then?"

languages.text: 「この件に関しては同意しよう。君の訪問が失敗に終われば、フットフォールはメチャクチャだ。そうなれば、君の好意はどうなる？」
languages.original_text: "In this matter, I would. If this visit of yours goes awry, it will destroy Footfall — what good will your favour do me then?"

traits.locale_text: 「この件に関しては同意しよう。君の訪問が失敗に終われば、フットフォールはメチャクチャだ。そうなれば、君の好意はどうなる？」

languages.text: “在这件事情上，我宁愿这么做。如果您出了什么差池，整个落脚港都会毁于一旦。到了那个时候，您的恩惠对我还能有什么好处呢？”
languages.original_text: "In this matter, I would. If this visit of yours goes awry, it will destroy Footfall — what good will your favour do me then?"

traits.locale_text: “在这件事情上，我宁愿这么做。如果您出了什么差池，整个落脚港都会毁于一旦。到了那个时候，您的恩惠对我还能有什么好处呢？”

languages.text: «En lo que a esto respecta, sí. Si esa visita suya sale mal, destruiría Paso. ¿De qué me serviría entonces su favor?».
languages.original_text: "In this matter, I would. If this visit of yours goes awry, it will destroy Footfall — what good will your favour do me then?"

traits.locale_text: «En lo que a esto respecta, sí. Si esa visita suya sale mal, destruiría Paso. ¿De qué me serviría entonces su favor?».

languages.text: « Sur ce point précis, oui. Si cette visite se passe mal, c'est la station entière qui sera détruite. À quoi me servirait votre aide, alors ? »
languages.original_text: "In this matter, I would. If this visit of yours goes awry, it will destroy Footfall — what good will your favour do me then?"

traits.locale_text: « Sur ce point précis, oui. Si cette visite se passe mal, c'est la station entière qui sera détruite. À quoi me servirait votre aide, alors ? »

languages.text: "In dieser Angelegenheit schon. Wenn Euer Besuch scheitert, wird Footfall zerstört – und was bringt mir dann Eure Gunst?"
languages.original_text: "In this matter, I would. If this visit of yours goes awry, it will destroy Footfall — what good will your favour do me then?"

languages.text: "Bu konuda çıkmak durumundayım. Bu ufak ziyaretiniz ters giderse Binliman'ın sonu gelir. O zaman yardımınızın bana ne faydası olacak?"
languages.original_text: "In this matter, I would. If this visit of yours goes awry, it will destroy Footfall — what good will your favour do me then?"

traits.locale_text: "Bu konuda çıkmak durumundayım. Bu küçük teşebbüsünüz ters giderse Binliman yok olur. O zaman da kimsenin kimseye borcu kalmaz."
